This is a basic full stack application from Galvanize
(http://www.galvanize.com/learn/learn-to-code/build-full-stack-app-40-minutes/)
In order to run this app you will need to do the following:
Install Homebrew:
/usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"

Install Node:
brew install node

Install Sqlite
brew install sqlite3

From the main dir (/ideaKeeper)
npm init
npm install express body-parser sqlite knex --save
node server.js

Open your browser and navigate to localhost:3000
